Two points.  <br><br>
I disagree with your opinion about the third world doctors.  My area of the world substantiates the problem.  Maybe yours doesn't.  Consider yourself lucky and at least understand that the Vet is treated as a substandard species.  The VA is no exception.<br><br>
I agree with you about Iraq and have posted this opinion before.  An exception.  The words mass murder when applied to the requirements of war disturbs me and brings back all those memories of the NAM protestors.<br><br>
